frc.team670.robot.commands.climb.pistonClimb

Class AbortRobotPistonClimb

  • java.lang.Object
    • InstantCommand
      • frc.team670.robot.commands.climb.pistonClimb.AbortRobotPistonClimb

  • public class AbortRobotPistonClimb
extends InstantCommand
    Command to run if there is very little time left in the match, and the driver just wants to bring the robot down. If the front pistons have been partially retracted, it will deploy them to match the back pistons, then it will bring the robot down
